title: Serpent and Fruit

description:
Oblong, with curved corners and sides, top edge slightly concave, bottom slightly convex, box narrows slightly towards bottom, featuring serpent crawling up left side of case body, tail wrapped around branch, coiled at top, on lid, with mouth open adjacent to piece of fruit. 
Reverse identical. Striker on bottom.
